姦，而美國則有5份1女性反映被強姦過。反映有被強姦經歷的日本女性中，逾3份2人從未告訴家人或朋友，只有34%人說有報警。</strong><br />\n<br />\n早稻田大學性別法律講師谷田川知惠（Tomoe Yatagawa）指：「（社會）對女性的偏見根深蒂固，而且非常嚴重，人們根本不把性犯罪的危害當成一回事。」上智大學政治學教授三浦麻里（Mari Miura）亦稱：「<strong>我認為日本民眾對同意的含義缺乏意識，而日本男性就從中獲利。</strong>」<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"Rape culture 賴落虛擬作品度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本都識自己迫害自己創作者啦"},{"pid":"4789def36de10be5ff334aa3c36fe2a80d167164","tid":530723,"uid":26506,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f87d19d263352cb2dd5387d177ee080029fa8312","tid":530723,"uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"64fd40951b29b6d29f40a699ee11dac83a1a3b1a","tid":530723,"uid":33357,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T05:06:26.000Z","msg":"日本真係唔同國際<br />\n個個#metoo<br />\n佢地就相反"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"亞洲大部分國家都係咁..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T05:19:21.000Z","msg":"韓國嘅feminist體現到各走極端有幾煩"},{"pid":"d9662f89b61510c6d56dc5a2fcbe1c50ddc6cd80","tid":530723,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T05:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bb1bfa55411e20915a530c926f22891d9da3f8","tid":530723,"uid":139815,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T05:20:15.000Z","msg":"日本萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c6c502726d229667ce5eedd332d6e4089b255e","tid":530723,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f87d19d263352cb2dd5387d177ee080029fa8312","tid":530723,"uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"64fd40951b29b6d29f40a699ee11dac83a1a3b1a","tid":530723,"uid":33357,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T05:06:26.0